data.description: Bonita is so Neat-a! Long time owner. Neat and clean and very well maintained. The whole interior of home has been freshly painted, even the basement floor. Thermal windows. Half bath on main level. Eat-in kitchen with dishwasher, breakfast bar and built in microwave. Separate dining room, four bedrooms (one has a real small closet) all bedrooms are upstairs. Between the living room and dining room is a built in bookcase. The electric box was replace in 1/09. The seller is offering a home protection plan. The dining room set stays with the house, table with a leaf, 6 chairs, china cabinet and hutch.
